  (string?)
  #:category font
  "
@cindex simple text strings

A simple text string; @code{\\markup @{ foo @}} is equivalent with
@code{\\markup @{ \\simple #\"foo\" @}}.

Note: for creating standard text markup or defining new markup commands,
